frames.caption: A surreal creature, combining features of a bear and a whale, floats majestically over a lush, green valley surrounded by towering mountains. The creature's body resembles a whale with flippers, while its head is distinctly bear-like. The scene is set against a backdrop of snow-capped peaks under a clear blue sky.
frames.description: The image depicts a fantastical scene where a hybrid animal, part bear and part whale, appears to be flying over a picturesque mountain valley. The setting is serene and otherworldly, with vibrant green meadows and distant snowy mountains.

frames.description: The scene depicts a whimsical and imaginative setting where a hybrid creature, part whale and part bear, glides through a picturesque valley. The backdrop features towering mountains with snowy peaks, while the foreground is filled with verdant fields and scattered farmhouses.
